- \`t(key, params?): string\` - Translate a key
- \`setLanguage(lang): Promise<void>\` - Set language
- \`getLanguage(): string\` - Get current language
- \`has(key): boolean\` - Check if translation exists
- \`clearCache(): void\` - Clear translation cache
